18 17-7-209 to the firefighting training facility infrastructure account established in [section 2].
19
20 NEW SECTION. Section 8. Appropriation. There is appropriated $5 million from the firefighting
21 training facility infrastructure account established in [section 2] to the department of military affairs for the
22 biennium beginning July 1, 2025, for grants authorized in [sections 3 through 5]. Appropriations are authorized
23 to continue through the biennium beginning July 1, 2029.
24
25 NEW SECTION. Section 9. Effective date. [This act] is effective July 1 JUNE 30, 2025.
26
27 NEW SECTION. Section 10. Termination. [This act] terminates June 30, 2031.
